{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "5240d3b8-013b-4e5c-968e-dacea7b64463", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5240d3b8-013b-4e5c-968e-dacea7b64463@1.pkg/1772597586178/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597586555", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5240d3b8-013b-4e5c-968e-dacea7b64463@1.pkg/1772597586178/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597586555"}, "identifier": "5240d3b8-013b-4e5c-968e-dacea7b64463", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①：题干中的食品安全抽检是市场监管职责，通过抽查保障食品安全，故①符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>②：公正司法是司法机关（如法院、检察院）的职责，而北京市市场监督管理部门属于行政机关，故②说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>③：北京市市场监督管理部门通过征集民意、针对性抽检和信息公开，体现了主动担当、服务人民的宗旨，符合建设服务型政府的要求，故③符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>④：检察权由检察机关独立行使，行政机关无此职权，故④说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选B。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025北京中考真题）作为行政机关的北京市市场监督管理部门广泛开展食品安全“你点我检”服务活动，2025年1—5月，已累计征集市民“点检”意见4.5万次，针对群众关注度较高的食品，完成针对性抽检1.8万批次，抽检结果信息通过政务网站及时公开发布。这体现北京市市场监督管理部门（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">①认真履行监管职能，保障食品安全</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">②提升公正司法实效，回应民生关切</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">③敢担当，建设人民满意的服务型政府</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">④独立行使检察权，维护社会公平正义</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025北京中考真题）作为行政机关的北京市市场监督管理部门广泛开展食品安全“你点我检”服务活动，2025年1—5月，已累计征集市民“点检”意见4.5万次，针对群众关注度较高的食品，完成针对性抽检1.8万批次，抽检结果信息通过政务网站及时公开发布。这体现北京市市场监督管理部门（   ）①认真履行监管职能，保障食品安全②提升公正司法实效，回应民生关切③敢担当，建设人民满意的服务型政府④独立行使", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5240d3b8-013b-4e5c-968e-dacea7b64463@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754818226654", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②&nbsp;</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①③&nbsp;</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②④ &nbsp;</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编·2025北京中考真题）作为行政机关的北京市市场监督管理部门广泛开展食品安全“你点我检”服务活动，2025年1—5月，已累计征集市民“点检”意见4.5万次，针对群众关注度较高的食品，完成针对性抽检1.8万批次，抽检结果信息通过政务网站及时公开发布。这体现北京市市场监督管理部门（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">①认真履行监管职能，保障食品安全</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">②提升公正司法实效，回应民生关切</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">③敢担当，建设人民满意的服务型政府</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">④独立行使检察权，维护社会公平正义</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-8